Barboach (TCG)

From Bulbapedia, the community-driven Pokémon encyclopedia.
Jump to navigationJump to search
← #0338: Solrock
Pokémon
#0340: Whiscash →
For Pokémon TCG Pocket cards, see Barboach (TCG Pocket).

Barboach has been featured on 9 different cards since it debuted in the EX Dragon expansion of the Pokémon Trading Card Game. Barboach cards are normally Water-type or Fighting-type Basic Pokémon.

List of Pokémon cards featuring Barboach

Barboach
Cards listed with a blue background are only legal to use in the current Expanded format.
Cards listed with a green background are legal to use in both the current Standard and Expanded formats.
